channel.title: [DELTA]::teleto command?[DELTA]
channel.description: Ok, I have a DELTA server, and bluur's client, but I can not find out where my ::teleto command is. I checked in client.java on both, client and server side. I can't seem to find the code, but the command works for admins+ so It must be coded somewhere? I want to edit this code so I can make it teleport me to a different height, because right now, it only teleports me to absX and absY. I want it to teleport me to absX absY height. Can someone tell me where this command is located? I can't find it anywhere. [I DID DO CTRL+F AND SEARCH "TELETO" IT STILL DID NOT FIND ANYTHING IN CLIENT.JAVA ON CLIENT, OR SERVER SIDE.]

item.title: [DELTA]::teleto command?[DELTA]
item.dc:creator: @riku9182 riku9182
item.description:
@riku9182 wrote:

Go into client.java in your server and add this

    if (command.startsWith("tele") && playerRights >= 1) {
        	String[] args = command.split(" ");
        	if(args.length == 3) {
                int newPosX = Integer.parseInt(args[1]);
                int newPosY = Integer.parseInt(args[2]);
                toX = newPosX;
                toY = newPosY;
    }

}

Hope i helped
